description:
In this video we breakdown, explain, review, and recap Season 3 Episode 6 "Decoherence" of HBO's Westworld for new theories, easter eggs, and details you missed. We'll explore who might help Maeve and what happened to Charlotte Hale. The new season stars Aaron Paul, Evan Rachel Wood, Ed Harris and Jeffrey Wright.
